# Optional: directory for the Chinese release note written to a personal knowledge base.
# After a successful release (see .claude/commands/release.md → "Update notes"), the
# Chinese update note is appended to $CC_RELEASE_NOTES_DIR/更新说明.md, newest on top.
# Leave empty (or omit .env entirely) to skip this step — it never blocks the release.
CC_RELEASE_NOTES_DIR=
